title: Lars Andersen: Ultimate Zombie Apocalypse Archery.

media:group.media:title: Lars Andersen: Ultimate Zombie Apocalypse Archery.
media:group.media:description:
Terminate zombies with 4 inch cut arrows!

I was going to make a fun Halloween video
and Zombie Apocalypse is really funny, I thought.
Many are writing funny comments about the Zombie Apocalypse team on my video.

And although I actually liked Zombi movies and books
then the whole concept of totally stupid and slow zombies
is actually very little dangerous.

I got my blacksmith to make some oversized 4" cutting arrows, razor sharp!!

Sincerely
Lars Andersen
